{"tid":1771114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（最後7天）安怡稱將市民反TVB訴求向部門反映 至今近月仍未回應","createTime":"2019-12-05T15:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T15:36:37.000Z","uid":75759,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c624ebac5b733e6389a64a84615fee877b50b33a","tid":1771114,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">品牌負資產</span></span></strong>，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">品牌形象將付諸流水</span></span></strong>！無人可憐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB今個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到年底啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga<br />\n<br />\n是晚精選@5 DEC 2019 <br />\n安怡<br />\n是晚精選@5/12<br />\n💎 安怡 💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/Anlenehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FAnlenehk%2F&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=3b6105cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/Anlenehk/</a><br />\n👆去派嬲兼留言👆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gRppGs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gRppGs.jpg&h=b18ee2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n💢 拖字訣 謹以罐頭回應敷衍市民 💢<br />\n面對市民對其TVB廣告的質疑，安怡一律以罐頭回應敷衍了事，直到現在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">超過3週仍未見任何回應或跟進行動</span></strong>，廣告亦繼續於TVB播放中！<br />\n<br />\n❓ 標榜含葡萄糖胺強關節 缺臨床實驗證明❓<br />\n👇一齊睇吓消費者委員會點講👇<br />\n<br />\n「研究發現4種常見的成分和相關的健康聲稱，只有奧米加3脂肪酸和奧米加6脂肪酸對於心臟健康的效益，獲廣泛的臨床研究證實，也獲得美國、歐盟等地的官方機構接納。至於其他聲稱包括益生菌與腸道健康、提升抵抗力、增加鈣質吸收；葡萄糖胺與關節健康；膽鹼與增強記憶，則全部缺乏足夠或一致的臨床實驗結果證實效益。」<br />\n<br />\n❓補鈣強健骨骼對抗流失？❓<br />\n安怡2倍鈣對抗35歲後骨質密度改變<br />\n專科醫生黃仕雄：35歲後骨質已不可存於骨骼<br />\n<br />\n [Source]<br />\n醫生拆解四大補鈣迷思 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2r2MymL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r2MymL&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=968f0abb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2r2MymL</a><br />\n專家： 多數長者奶粉健康聲稱冇足夠數據支持 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2RomE7L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RomE7L&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=fca7cec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2RomE7L</a><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再唔撤budget，業績定仆直！<br />\n盡快同TVB割席！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n基本：<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.互Like留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階：<br />\n4. 放張抵制圖留言以示不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n※請善用template，清晰表達訴求<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=a1cc8114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=987632ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道（已被封<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=966d029f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 繼續狙擊頻道（後備channel，請follow）: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb2&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=fc3f8694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb2</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=c616350c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a>"},{"pid":"a3c05818f278a39928b8a2e90aeb2142d6dfe6c4","tid":1771114,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b12a48d1086f4b88dc93acb7d2c150985eeccad3","tid":1771114,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1de1ceed5d10334af071f9a0e5021c3135496b54","tid":1771114,"uid":259856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3a2b2dac0e8746766b33d3abfcb595e54652f4d1","tid":1771114,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責"},{"pid":"295cfb42bc8b33baf7828aa67fb604aa8a0e4f5b","tid":1771114,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4e38c84ea25610f6729036cc1d48ae440d0a2d4","tid":1771114,"uid":165127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c8875f18698c475df30d24666fa4301d5e893dd1","tid":1771114,"uid":224869,"like":0,"